description: Program that rapidly attacks wherever you look.

name: fly.lua
description: Input a impulse strength, shift to boost, space to jump-boost.

description: follow a target Ex: follow 0.5 NullHarp.

description: Tells you how much damage you took in the last tick.

name: hover.lua
description: Hover at a specified Y-Level Ex: hover 60

description: Forcibly look at a target, Ex: look NullHarp

description: Experimental program to receive json format projected builds

description: Experimental program to send json format projected builds

description: tracks all entities in nearby area, marks with color and text threw walls.
